ne;\"><a id=\"11_nwl\" href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=0&amp;jk=f85b260a37fd4687&amp;k=%B9%A4%B3%CC&amp;k0=%B9%A4%B3%CC&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=3&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=52066088_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=8746fd37a265bf8&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1847666&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Exzbu%2Ecom%2F2%2Fview%2D4123641%2Ehtm&amp;urlid=0\" target=\"_blank\" mpid=\"11\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;text-decoration:none;color:#336699;\" data_ue_src=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=0&amp;jk=f85b260a37fd4687&amp;k=%B9%A4%B3%CC&amp;k0=%B9%A4%B3%CC&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=3&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=52066088_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=8746fd37a265bf8&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1847666&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Exzbu%2Ecom%2F2%2Fview%2D4123641%2Ehtm&amp;urlid=0\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;color:#0000FF;width:auto;height:auto;\">工程</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:25.200000762939453px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">类别、施工条件等综合考虑报价策略，研究工程的性质和特点，按工程量变化的趋势调整单价，制定合理的价位区间，最后根据投标经验确定投标价。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;line-height:1.2em;font-family:arial, 宋体;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:25.200000762939453px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">　　(4)认真参加现场考察和标前会议,针对招标文件中出现的差异进行提问。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;line-height:1.2em;font-family:arial, 宋体;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:25.200000762939453px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">　　(5)合理使用辅助手段中标，如采用技术交流，许诺优惠条件，选择合适的投标代理人，均是投标的辅助手段。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;line-height:1.2em;font-family:arial, 宋体;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:25.200000762939453px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">　　2、报价策略方面&nbsp;</span><br sty